item.name: Available Real Size
item.description: The amount of real/physical memory currently unused or available.

item.name: Total RAM Free
item.description: The total amount of memory free or available for use on this host. This value typically covers both real memory and swap space or virtual memory.

trigger.name: CPU Overloaded on {HOST.NAME} Idle = {ITEM.VALUE}
trigger.description: CPU Idle below 15% for last 15 minutes.

trigger.name: Low free RAM({ITEM.VALUE}) on {HOST.NAME}
trigger.description: Free memory below 15% for last 15 minutes.
